Name: Super Lobster Run
About the game: Super Lobster Run is a Feel-Good Fun and Exciting Lobster Runner Game! Playing as Laughy the Lobster you are chased out of the ocean by a deadly shark and must sidestep obstacles and travel through dangerous regions to reach safety! FEATURES - Easy to Play (Dodge Left or Right) - Travel Through Unique and Beautiful Regions - Highly Animated - Play with Controller - Models are Hand Sculpt then Painted with 4k Textures and Animated - The Most Fun You'll Have Being a Lobster!
